track_notes: A 3.4 mile loop hike with 1050 EG starting from Indian Grave Gap combining the Appalachian Trail, the Rocky Mtn Trail and a short hike along FS Road 283. This provides a bit more knee friendly descent along the Rocky Mtn trail than returning down the many steps on the AT.

As another alternative, you can hike on the Rocky Mtn trail from Indian Grave Gap Rd/FS Road 283.  Hike is 1.6 miles with 1000 EG.  At mile 1.1, take a left on the AT (north-bound) for the final 1/2 mile to the summit.
track_title: W4G/NG-011 Rocky Mtn via Rocky Mtn Trail
